697
00:45:35,796 --> 00:45:37,812
- consider the challenge.
- Challenge?

698
00:45:37,876 --> 00:45:40,148
Think what cleverness
it would take...

699
00:45:40,212 --> 00:45:41,940
to wean him from his madness.

700
00:45:42,004 --> 00:45:43,476
Turn him from his course.

701
00:45:43,540 --> 00:45:46,100
To persuade him
to come back home.

702
00:45:46,164 --> 00:45:49,172
To bring him to see
the same world?

703
00:45:49,236 --> 00:45:51,892
Hmm. That is a challenge.

704
00:45:51,956 --> 00:45:53,332
Enormous.

705
00:45:53,396 --> 00:45:55,444
To work within his lunacy...

706
00:45:55,508 --> 00:45:58,676
to cure him through
the very terms that are his own.

707
00:46:00,308 --> 00:46:02,164
Come, father. We shall do it.

708
00:46:03,444 --> 00:46:06,836
