If you keep interrupting me
like this...

750
00:47:55,477 --> 00:47:57,013
the whole thing will be gone
right out of my head.

751
00:47:57,077 --> 00:48:00,245
- Well, what's he want?
- I'm getting to it.

752
00:48:00,309 --> 00:48:01,429
I beg thee grant
that I may kiss

753
00:48:01,493 --> 00:48:04,213
The nethermost hem
of thy garment

754
00:48:04,277 --> 00:48:07,861
And send to me a token
of thy fair esteem

755
00:48:07,925 --> 00:48:12,949
That I may carry
as my standard into battle

756
